Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切记切记  不要给我捅娄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说
