Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名射手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到不必每天看到你的那张脸
