Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是几乎每天都和老师碰面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  为什么
