Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  balsamico醋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假里平常没什么事情做  好闲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一不注意就开始了懒散的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘻嘻嘻  既然你这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后不会再讲「作业借我抄」之类的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很可爱呢
