Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  老师上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放假之后上线频率很高嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正时间充裕要不要去刷怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在乔布伦村附近的洞窟里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在传送门附近等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…在网络世界里就别每天都把现实中的话题扯出来好不好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像每天被小镜训一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  今天热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  欢迎  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把电风扇拿出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为很热嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先坐那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你绝对会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  此方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么早安啊  你以为现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来还真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…一般人都会做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小镜今早不也做过了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,COMP祭  评价好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:25.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(COMP祭，第N次对这个词注解…月刊comptio上定期举办的限量商品贩卖活动\N话说这次封面竟然是Fate)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收集这个杂志相关单行本的调查问卷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能换取许多限定品的点数卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好像被吸引一般买了许多单行本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也说过类似的关于点数卡的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人真是对礼品还有限定物没什么抵抗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说备足保存用  观赏用  布教用才是基本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着！你毫无疑问是个特殊的例子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都不会有你这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外也会有忘记借给谁最后只好重新买的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  老问题还是拜托你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  作业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白的地方我教你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也自己去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,balsamuco醋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小镜  这里教我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小镜  从这到这我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小镜  这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你自己根本没动脑子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是这之后的全都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你自己完全没动脑子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没教我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵  我来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  唯姐  来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你教教我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  数学作业吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个？包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  作为一个保护好孩子的警官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这么做对自己不好所以不能光是依赖别人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好多地方都不懂  烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要随便写一点差不多的答案不就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正作业只要能交就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  原来如此  好聪明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  她刚才说的话突然让人感觉好假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉那样对自己也没什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我以前也这样做过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喘口气稍微玩下网络游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:17:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去打怪30分正好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,30分左右的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,独身打怪去吧  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯  在世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯嗯  变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为谁而嗯嗯嗯嗯～
